// Boot Directly to Desktop
// HPH Knowledgebase -RasPi
// Fluvio L. Lobo Fenoglietto

// Follow this guide in order have Raspian boot directly into its main UI...\

1.0- On the terminal, call raspberry configuration

> sudo raspi-config

2.0- Select option #3 - "Eanable Boot to Desktop/Scratch"

3.0- Select option #2 - "Desktop Log in as user 'pi' at the graphical desktop"


// References

> http://raspberrypi.stackexchange.com/questions/7261/how-to-set-my-raspberry-pi-to-boot-into-the-gui